txt.en: Supply-stores can be found hidden throughout Osgiliath.\n\nEchil has asked you to seek out hidden supply-stores and return them to the Rangers of Ithilien within Osgiliath.
'There are many to look after down here, [placeholder]. You have made that task far easier this day.\n\n'You have my thanks.'
Echil can be found in the tunnels beneath Osgiliath.\n\nYou have recovered many hidden supply-stores from Osgiliath, and should now deliver them to Echil.
Trapped within the tunnels below Osgiliath, the Rangers of Ithilien struggle to survive as their supplies dwindle.
Deliver the recovered goods to Echil

'As with weapons and healing herbs, we have hidden numerous supply-stores throughout the city containing rations and fresh water.

'If our stay in this sunken labyrinth is to be a lengthy one, we will have need of those supplies.

'Travel to the surface and search throughout the city for our supply-stores. When you have found as many as you can bear, return them to me!'
